data.description: This charming, comfortable home can be yours for under 400k.  Upgrades throughout - plank tile flooring in living room and family room, vaulted ceilings.  The kitchen has beautifully upgraded wood-stained cabinets that are staggered, granite counters with a decorative backsplash, stainless steel appliances and a large island.  Separate living room and great room. Hallway has a built-in desk area.  Sit outside in your backyard and enjoy great mountain views.  Pavers and easy to care for artificial grass.  Storage shed.  Leased solar allows for low energy bills.  Buckeye is considered one of the fastest growing cities in the country!  Close to I-10, new Costco now open.  Coming in 2024:  Verrado Marketplace and an Abrazo medical campus.  Lots of fun things happening.  Don't miss this one!
